# prompts/_dispatch/

Two layers for every worker send:

1. **Role** cheatsheet (why: execute / plan / audit)
2. **Model shape** (`model-shapes.md`) + **algorithm** (`dispatch-algorithm.md`)

| File | What |
|------|------|
| executor-cheatsheet.md | Task → Done → Autonomy (role) |
| orchestrator-cheatsheet.md | Goal → Context → Done (role) |
| auditor-cheatsheet.md | What → Where → Readiness (role) |
| flash-cheatsheet.md | One-shot (role) |
| model-shapes.md | DeepSeek / GLM / Grok / **GPT-5.6** skeletons |
| dispatch-algorithm.md | **Mandatory** role → family → shape → pin → send |

Before send: open `dispatch-algorithm.md`, pick family, fill that family's skeleton, pin CLI+model+effort, write brief under `waves/<id>/prompts/`.

GPT-5.6: Goal + Success + Stop (lean). Official: https://developers.openai.com/api/docs/guides/prompt-guidance-gpt-5p6

Do not paste full AGENTS.md into every dispatch.
